race.comment: CATCH SOME RAYS (4) shapes well for this after finishing second last start over 350m at this track but in a scintillating 18.84 behind Mile A Minute. Rates a top chance if runs up to latest. SHORT STRAW TREV (8) has a strong record this journey here with five wins and a minor from nine starts. Was out of the placings last time (23.19) at Warragul in a Grade 4/5, finishing seventh and beaten 6 lengths. Makes strong appeal on best. FLAMING FOX (2) finished second last start over 350m at this track but was game in defeat in a fast 19.22. Has the ability and can measure up. WILD SERENA (1) is always a threat when she races at this track and distance.
